data.text: ever experience eating in the pool? here is it. one eighty coffee restaurant - one of best spot to go for unique ambiance. having a lunch in a pool is such a new experience. another bandung, indonesia great place to put in your bucketlist if you be there for a vacation. overall the food taste nice. there is also indoor if you don't want to be in the water and the indoor ambience is nice too. @oneeightycoffee  1. lasagna l'uovo - lasagna served with poached egg, tomato sauce, mix sauce, and cheese sauce. 2. salmon diavolo - pasta with olive oil, salmon, lime leaves, black olive, chili padi, tomato and dill. 3. chicken wings - marinated chicken wings served with spicy honey sauce. love it overall.
